    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public class BlueprintsTinkerConfig
extends BaseBlueprintsConfig<BlueprintsTinkerConfig>
    A Config that creates Blueprints TinkerGraph specific configuration.

    All features are all optional: configuration can be created using all or none of them.
